## Bug #1 Fixed: Webhook Body Parsing (Step 3)

`express.json()` was before the webhook route, destroying the raw body needed for Stripe signature verification.

```diff
-app.use(express.json());  // line 21
-// ... 400 lines later ...
-app.post('/api/payment/webhook', ...)  // too late!
+// Webhook FIRST
+app.post('/api/payment/webhook', express.raw(...), ...);
+// THEN JSON parsing
+app.use(express.json());
```

Also made Stripe init resilient — server no longer crashes without keys.

